==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fifteen
<hw>Fif"teen`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>fiftene</ets>, AS. <ets>f⟦imac⟧ft⟦ymac⟧ne</ets>,
<ets>f⟦imac⟧ft⟦emac⟧ne</ets>. See <er>Five</er>, and <er>Ten</er>, and
cf. <er>Fifty</er>.]</ety> <def>Five and ten; one more than
fourteen.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fifteen</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Fifteen
<hw>Fif"teen`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The sum of five and
ten; fifteen units or objects.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A symbol representing fifteen units, as 15, or
xv.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fifteenth</ent>⟦br⟧
